\f0\fs24 \cf0 About the Center... 
\b (home page body copy)
\b0 \
\
Welcome to Studio Bamboo Institute of Yoga and Teacher Training School located in the Marina Shores\
Shoppes in Virginia Beach, Virginia. Studio Bamboo is committed to providing our community the most\
enriching and informative yoga program available. Our instructional staff is dedicated to providing an\
unparalleled experience in yoga. .\
\
Studio Bamboo is a spacious and tranquil Yoga Center, offering three rooms for practice, a beautiful retail\
and sitting space, and restrooms including showers. Our interior was designed specifically to step away from\
the hustle and bustle of our busy world. When you step into the Center you will immediately feel taken away\
with the serene colors, high ceilings, accents, and beautiful bamboo and flowing river rock floors. The design\
of all areas support the desire for energy flow and a balance of yin and yang energies, giving you a calm and\
nurturing space to practice.\
\
\
About our classes 
\b (classes home page)
\b0 \
\
Classes at Studio Bamboo range from gentle to challenging, from relaxing restorative classes to the most\
intense practice imaginable. We also offers specialized classes in kids, teens, pre-natal, post-natal, yoga for\
therapy (rehabilitative) & adaptive yoga, yoga for athletes, seniors, hot classes, even laughter yoga, you will\
find them all and even more at Studio Bamboo. If you are new to yoga or a seasoned practitioner you will find a\
class to meet your needs at our Center.\
\
In addition to our regularly scheduled classes Studio Bamboo will also facilitate workshops and seminars\
throughout the year by our own instructional staff as well as internationally known yogis, check our events page\
for more information.\
\
