\b Business / Corporate Classes\

\b0 \
Let Studio Bamboo help to make your business more effective by assisting your employees/teams with on-site\
and studio based classes. A workplace yoga program is a fabulous opportunity to bring the ancient practices\
of yoga into the office. Studio Bamboo can help your business by using yoga to work with issues related to\
physical and mental health, stress management, focus, productivity, and efficient decision making just to name\
a few. We can offer yoga classes in the workplace (if space available), yoga in chairs, one time seminars,\
special day long seminars for total well being, weekend retreats, and many more possibilities. Please e-mail or\
call to inquire.\
\
