\b Private Classes
\b0 \
\
The study of yoga began as a dialog between teacher and student. Studio Bamboo honors that tradition by\
offering Private Yoga Instruction for individual students or small groups. This is a great way to meet your\
individual needs for that body-mind connection, relaxation and stress management. We recommend private\
instruction for those who are new to yoga, those with injuries or specific limitations, or for those who wish to\
have a specialized consultation regarding your yoga practice. These sessions may take place in the Center or\
off-site. Privates can be scheduled as one-on-one, duets, or semi-privates. Studio Bamboo wants you to have\
the best experience possible so choosing the right teacher is important, let us help. With time and location, rates\
vary, please call or e-mail to inquire.\
